title: USGS, M 1+ earthquakes, World, 12.22.08 through 12.29.08
name: USGS, M 1+ earthquakes, World, 12.22.08 through 12.29.08
description: This datasets displays the locations of all recorded earthquakes of a magnitude of 1 or greater around the world from the period of 12.22.08 through 12.29.08. The findings are from the US Geological Survey (USGS). Earthquake information is extracted from a merged catalog of earthquakes located by the USGS and contributing networks. Earthquakes will be broadcast within a few minutes for California events and within 30-minutes for world-wide events.
